  "title": "WAITER/WAITERESS",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duties of Service Crew</strong></p><ul><li>Provide excellent customer service experience.</li><li>Maintain the stock service areas with supplies such as condiments and tableware’s</li><li>Assist in making hot and cold beverages</li><li>Assist in serving food and beverage to guest</li><li>Assist in Packing food orders in Kitchen for both dine in, online & takeaway orders</li><li>Assist in Taking Order</li><li>Assist in Seating guest</li><li>Assist in keeping the restaurant clean at all times</li><li>Assist in clearing tables , sweeping , mopping etc</li><li>Provide menu recommendations appropriately</li><li>Attend to customers’ needs promptly and professionally</li><li>Adhere to personal & food safety procedures</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and the hygiene of the restaurant</li><li>Perform any other duties assigned by Manager</li></ul>",
